Blu Ray Babes consists of a collection of Glamour / Girl Girl video scenes shot in the 90s by Julie Strain and Monique Gabrielle. It was maintained in its original 4:3 cut. The dvd has about 7 "fantasy sequences" and 12 behind the scenes short videos of a photo shoot with Julie K Smith and Julie Strain. The fantasy sequences contain Julie and Monique fully nude doing mostly simulated sex scenes. This was the norm for these videos at the time with a musical overlay and the ladies posing and modeling nude. The quality of the video is ok to slightly poor. Recommended to fans of Julie and Monique. Julie Smith unfortunately only appears in the extras
